XML-Writer-Simple
=================

XML-Writer-Simple is a simple Perl module to write XML. It takes some
ideas from CGI and applies them for the XML World.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


